'''David Dorfman''' (born February 7, 1993) is an [[United States|American]] [[teen actor]]. His most notable role was as Aidan Keller in the 2002 [[horror film]] remake ''[[The Ring (2002 film)|The Ring]]'', and its 2005 sequel ''[[The Ring Two]]''. He has also appeared in the 2000 film ''[[Panic (2000 film)|Panic]]'' as Sammy. Some people may remember him as the character "[[Charles Wallace Murry]]" in the film version of ''[[A Wrinkle in Time]]''. In 2008, Dorfman appeared in the film ''[[Drillbit Taylor]]''. He will be co-starring, along with Thomas Haden Church in ''[http://www.fearnet.com/news/b17665_fearnet_announces_next_original_zombie.html Zombie Roadkill]''. Dorfman is also currently a student at UCLA (University of California, Los Angeles).
